<br /><br />
In my current role at HSBC as an operations management trainee, I work extensively with Excel VBA to build spreadsheet applications for standardising operating procedures, automating repetitive tasks and analysing business data. I think many of you will find Excel and VBA useful in your career as well. While VBA is not considered a mainstream programming language - itâ€™s not as sexy as Python - it definitely worth learning.
<br /><br />
